In this program, we’re using a function named generateResource() to create a smart pointer encapsulated resource, which is then passed back to function main(). Function main() then assigns that to an existing Auto_ptr3 object.When this program is run, it prints:Resource acquired
Resource acquired
Resource destroyed
Resource acquired
Resource destroyed
